Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.50,0:01:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼突然改變了決定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.90,0:01:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手公主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還想殺了我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.20,0:01:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你可是100%信任啊 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.70,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對我的絕對忠心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及識破綱手企圖殺我的眼力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢當 畢竟我也是醫療班出身的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她剛才的查克拉充滿了殺氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手 我可是真心想讓他們兩個復活哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還答應了你不動木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那是你的花言巧語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常想見他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面 我也想見見他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面 我也想抱抱他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是一面 我也想看看他們的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我即將看到繩樹和斷的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一瞬間 我突然發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發覺自己是一個多沒用的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要一想到他們的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然就會全然不顧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜歡他們 真心愛他們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想再次擁抱他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對…不會輸給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當我看到那個小鬼後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起了他們兩人的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我打算忘記的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個村子是爺爺的寶貝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保護它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是創立了這個村子的初代火影的孫子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜歡這個村子 還有我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想要保護他們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要像爺爺那樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚會繼承火影的稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你可不同 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 我要繼承火影之名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹死後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是靠這些回憶活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我一定要成為火影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為保護大家而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為火影是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人不惜賭上生命想去實現的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想幫他們實現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說過「有形之物早晚會凋零」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個想法不會凋零
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來交涉決裂了 沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣只能用力量逼你就範了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交涉決裂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說我至今好像還未和你交過手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您可真敢說啊 她的對手是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要將你們全部就地解決
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.10,0:06:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和以前一樣 力量還是那麼恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她打中一下就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.80,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡想拉開戰鬥距離有點擁擠
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算轉移
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣做會比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比較麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和綱手大人的手下在一起的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道什麼時候會前來援助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的麻煩人物是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和您以及綱手大人同為三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不會讓你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.76,0:07:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:08:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來那位綱手公主下手不輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 綱手大人拒絕他們的要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手婆婆到底去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:16.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是綱手大人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豚豚 在哪邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手的呼吸也變得急促了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.00,0:08:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體術並非我所長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵量丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個印是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個小鬼也會使用醫療忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肌肉被…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我切斷了您一部分的肱二頭肌和腿部肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就使不出那種恐怖的怪力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.20,0:09:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉手術刀 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不直接攻擊我的動脈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個手術刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可以在\N不留外傷的情況下切斷血管和肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.80,0:10:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在戰鬥中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有足夠的時間做出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以切斷動脈\N心臟等地的查克拉手術刀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過割斷對手的喉嚨還是沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 胸肌被切斷了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不是普通的醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施術的才能和效果遠超全盛期的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你死了可就麻煩了 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.66,0:10:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會割斷你喉嚨的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣你應該動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不簡單 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.91,0:11:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就因為呼吸困難而動彈不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來有必要讓她再吃些苦頭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不殺死她的前提下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明想動手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腳卻動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.10,0:11:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前這狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能使出這點力量嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.40,0:12:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她攻擊的不是我的肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是神經
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於發現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是神經
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.80,0:12:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把查克拉電子化 並將其電解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.00,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨後注入你的神經系統
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦和身體能夠進行交流
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.40,0:12:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是通過電子信號溝通
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手擾亂了時速360公里的運動電子信號
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她久疏陣地戰 居然還能保持這種實力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.50,0:12:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中的三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療術太消耗查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種狀態下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動右手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左腳就會動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動左腳腳踝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右肩就會動
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過怎麼移動想動的部位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.70,0:13:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經基本掌握了八成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為這種忍術
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能把我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就能活動身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是怕看到血嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓你看個夠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒見了 自來也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子啊 眼神那麼兇惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你們認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起參加了中忍考試
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.85,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼兜前輩會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙由我來搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.25,0:15:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你能活動身體也沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈活度不可能像之前那麼自如
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無路可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體終於恢復自如了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.05,0:15:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次面對兩個三忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.35,0:15:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少先幹掉一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼兜前輩和綱手婆婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真遲鈍啊 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你無法勝過佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看他的額頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是大蛇丸的部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.95,0:16:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我是音忍派來的間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢 騙人的吧 兜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.45,0:16:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中忍考試時 你教給我很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還經常幫助我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.85,0:16:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是為了收集你們的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集了你的相關數據後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不具備作為一個忍者的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和佐助不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是頭一次看到綱手大人這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.85,0:17:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再一個人逞強了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是您的手下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.15,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你再凶巴巴的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣可愛的下忍也不該來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對你體內寄生的怪物有點興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:18:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在傳說中的三忍面前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.65,0:18:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只不過如同一隻螻蟻一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你敢多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.45,0:18:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.55,0:18:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只右手動不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.15,0:18:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人一起攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從他無法防禦的右邊開始進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.05,0:18:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口針
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神經反射系統還沒完全恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.65,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲不開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中護額了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.15,0:19:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.65,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.25,0:19:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增血丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增血丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補充失去的血液
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.35,0:19:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小子跟我一樣 是醫療忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的血流得很是時候啊 兜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸大人 請拆下左手的繃帶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是…大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大終於出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼鏡的交給你處理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大蛇丸我來對付
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.85,0:22:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個混蛋叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.12,0:22:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想再對綱手婆婆下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.69,0:22:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要按照賭約
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.53,0:22:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個不吉利的首飾送給我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.77,0:22:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.06,0:22:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜大眼睛看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.42,0:22:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.80,0:22:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.57,0:23:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 憤怒的螺旋丸
